msgid "# Qwen3.6-35B-A3B Deployment Tutorial"
msgstr "# Qwen3.6-35B-A3B 部署教程"

msgid "## 1 Introduction"
msgstr "## 1 引言"

msgid ""
"Qwen3.6-35B-A3B is a sparse MoE model in the Qwen3.6 family, with 35B total "
"parameters and about 3B activated parameters per token. It uses the hybrid "
"attention architecture used by Qwen3.5-style models, and is suitable for "
"long-context online serving on Ascend hardware."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3.6-35B-A3B 是 Qwen3.6 系列中的稀疏 MoE 模型，总参数量为 35B，每个 token 激活约 3B 参数。它采用了 "
"Qwen3.5 风格模型使用的混合注意力架构，适用于在昇腾硬件上进行长上下文在线服务。"

msgid ""
"This document describes the main validation steps for the model, including "
"supported features, prerequisites, installation, single-node online "
"deployment, functional verification, accuracy and performance evaluation, "
"performance tuning, and FAQs."
msgstr "本文档描述了该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持特性、前提条件、安装、单节点在线部署、功能验证、精度与性能评估、性能调优以及常见问题解答。"

msgid ""
"The `Qwen3.6-35B-A3B` model is first supported in `vllm-ascend:v0.18.0rc1`. "
"Use `v0.18.0rc1` or later for this model. The examples below use the version"
" placeholder configured by the documentation build system."
msgstr ""
"`Qwen3.6-35B-A3B` 模型首次在 `vllm-ascend:v0.18.0rc1` 中得到支持。请使用 `v0.18.0rc1` "
"或更高版本。以下示例使用文档构建系统配置的版本占位符。"

msgid "## 2 Supported Features"
msgstr "## 2 支持特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix, including BF16, W8A8 quantization, chunked"
" prefill, automatic prefix caching, asynchronous scheduling, tensor "
"parallelism, expert parallelism, and ACLGraph support."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取模型的支持特性矩阵，包括"
" BF16、W8A8 量化、分块预填充、自动前缀缓存、异步调度、张量并行、专家并行以及 ACLGraph 支持。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get "
"feature configuration details."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性配置详情。"

msgid "## 3 Prerequisites"
msgstr "## 3 前提条件"

msgid "### 3.1 Model Weight"
msgstr "### 3.1 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `Qwen3.6-35B-A3B` (BF16 version): requires 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) node or 1 Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) node. [Download model weight](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B).\n"
"- `Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-w8a8` (quantized version): requires 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) node or 1 Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) node. [Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-w8a8)."
msgstr ""
"- `Qwen3.6-35B-A3B` (BF16 版本)：需要 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) 节点或 1 个 Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) 节点。[下载模型权重](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B)。\n"
"- `Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-w8a8` (量化版本)：需要 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) 节点或 1 个 Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) 节点。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-w8a8)。"

msgid "It is recommended to download the model weight to `/root/.cache/`."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到 `/root/.cache/`。"

msgid "## 4 Installation"
msgstr "## 4 安装"

msgid "### 4.1 Docker Image Installation"
msgstr "### 4.1 Docker 镜像安装"

msgid ""
"Select an image based on your machine type. For example, use "
"`quay.io/ascend/vllm-ascend:{{ vllm_ascend_version }}` for Atlas 800 A2 and "
"`quay.io/ascend/vllm-ascend:{{ vllm_ascend_version }}-a3` for Atlas 800 A3."
msgstr ""
"根据您的机器类型选择镜像。例如，Atlas 800 A2 使用 `quay.io/ascend/vllm-ascend:{{ "
"vllm_ascend_version }}`，Atlas 800 A3 使用 `quay.io/ascend/vllm-ascend:{{ "
"vllm_ascend_version }}-a3`。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [using docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-docker) for the "
