msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr "## 9 性能调优"

msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr "### 9.1 推荐配置"

msgid ""
"The following configurations are validated in specific test environments and"
" are for reference only. The optimal configuration depends on hardware type,"
" maximum input/output length, request concurrency, prefix cache hit rate, "
"and quantization. Tune the parameters in Section 9.2 based on your actual "
"workload."
msgstr ""
"以下配置在特定测试环境中经过验证，仅供参考。最佳配置取决于硬件类型、最大输入/输出长度、请求并发数、前缀缓存命中率和量化方式。请根据实际工作负载调整第9.2节中的参数。"

msgid "### 9.2 Tuning Guidelines"
msgstr "### 9.2 调优指南"

msgid ""
"Refer to [public performance tuning "
"documentation](../../developer_guide/performance_and_debug/optimization_and_tuning.md)"
" for general tuning methods, and refer to [feature "
"matrix](../../user_guide/support_matrix/feature_matrix.md) for feature "
"descriptions."
msgstr ""
"通用调优方法请参考[公开的性能调优文档](../../developer_guide/performance_and_debug/optimization_and_tuning.md)，功能描述请参考[特性矩阵](../../user_guide/support_matrix/feature_matrix.md)。"

msgid "Recommended tuning order:"
msgstr "推荐的调优顺序："

msgid ""
"1. Use single-node deployment. If more throughput is required, increase local DP groups within the same node.\n"
"2. Choose the maximum context length with `--max-model-len`. Long context increases KV cache usage, so reduce `--max-num-seqs` or `--gpu-memory-utilization` if OOM occurs.\n"
"3. Tune `--max-num-batched-tokens`. Larger values usually improve prefill throughput but increase activation memory. Decode-heavy workloads usually need smaller values.\n"
"4. Tune `--max-num-seqs` according to service concurrency. Requests above this value wait in the queue and the waiting time is counted in TTFT and TPOT.\n"
"5. Tune `--gpu-memory-utilization`. Increase it to provide more KV cache, but leave headroom for runtime memory fluctuation and expert imbalance.\n"
"6. Tune ACLGraph capture. `FULL_DECODE_ONLY` is recommended for decode. If you set `cudagraph_capture_sizes` manually, include common decode batch sizes. With FlashComm1, use capture sizes that are multiples of TP size."
msgstr ""
"1. 使用单节点部署。如果需要更高吞吐量，在同一节点内增加本地 DP 组。\n"
"2. 使用 `--max-model-len` 选择最大上下文长度。长上下文会增加 KV 缓存使用量，因此如果发生 OOM，请减少 `--max-num-seqs` 或 `--gpu-memory-utilization`。\n"
"3. 调整 `--max-num-batched-tokens`。较大的值通常会提高预填充吞吐量，但会增加激活内存。解码密集型工作负载通常需要较小的值。\n"
"4. 根据服务并发数调整 `--max-num-seqs`。超过此值的请求将在队列中等待，等待时间计入 TTFT 和 TPOT。\n"
"5. 调整 `--gpu-memory-utilization`。增加它以提供更多 KV 缓存，但需为运行时内存波动和专家不均衡预留空间。\n"
"6. 调整 ACLGraph 捕获。解码推荐使用 `FULL_DECODE_ONLY`。如果手动设置 `cudagraph_capture_sizes`，请包含常见的解码批次大小。使用 FlashComm1 时，请使用 TP 大小的整数倍作为捕获大小。"

msgid "### 9.3 Model-Specific Optimizations"
msgstr "### 9.3 模型特定优化"

msgid "## 10 FAQ"
msgstr "## 10 常见问题解答"

msgid ""
"For common environment, installation, and general parameter issues, refer to"
" [FAQs](../../faqs.md). This section only covers model-specific issues for "
"Qwen3.6-35B-A3B."
msgstr ""
"关于常见环境、安装和通用参数问题，请参考[常见问题](../../faqs.md)。本节仅涵盖 Qwen3.6-35B-A3B 的模型特定问题。"

msgid ""
"### Q1: Why does the service report OOM during startup or soon after "
"accepting requests?"
msgstr "### Q1：为什么服务在启动时或接受请求后不久报告 OOM？"

msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** The service fails during profile run, or it starts "
"successfully but reports OOM when real traffic arrives."
msgstr "**现象：** 服务在性能分析运行期间失败，或者成功启动但在真实流量到来时报告 OOM。"

msgid ""
"**Cause:** Qwen3.6 long-context serving consumes a large KV cache. Large "
"`--max-model-len`, large `--max-num-seqs`, large `--max-num-batched-tokens`,"
" or high `--gpu-memory-utilization` can leave insufficient HBM headroom."
msgstr ""
"**原因：** Qwen3.6 长上下文服务会消耗大量 KV 缓存。较大的 `--max-model-len`、`--max-num-"
"seqs`、`--max-num-batched-tokens` 或较高的 `--gpu-memory-utilization` 可能导致 HBM "
"余量不足。"

msgid ""
"**Solution:** Use the W8A8 model with `--quantization ascend` when possible,"
" lower `--max-model-len`, lower `--max-num-seqs`, lower `--max-num-batched-"
"tokens`, or reduce `--gpu-memory-utilization`. Keep "
"`PYTORCH_NPU_ALLOC_CONF=expandable_segments:True`."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 尽可能使用带有 `--quantization ascend` 的 W8A8 模型，降低 `--max-model-"
"len`、`--max-num-seqs`、`--max-num-batched-tokens`，或减少 `--gpu-memory-"
"utilization`。保持 `PYTORCH_NPU_ALLOC_CONF=expandable_segments:True`。"

msgid "### Q2: Why does enabling prefix caching not improve performance?"
msgstr "### Q2：为什么启用前缀缓存没有提升性能？"

msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** Prefix caching is enabled, but throughput or latency does "
"not improve."
msgstr "**现象：** 已启用前缀缓存，但吞吐量或延迟没有改善。"

msgid ""
"**Cause:** Prefix caching only helps when requests share reusable prefixes. "
"For random prompts or low cache hit rates, it may add memory pressure "
"without visible gains."
msgstr "**原因：** 前缀缓存仅在请求共享可重用前缀时才有帮助。对于随机提示或低缓存命中率，它可能会增加内存压力而没有明显收益。"

msgid ""
"**Solution:** Enable prefix caching for repeated-prefix workloads. For "
"random benchmark datasets or memory-constrained long-context workloads, "
"compare with `--no-enable-prefix-caching`."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 为重复前缀的工作负载启用前缀缓存。对于随机基准数据集或内存受限的长上下文工作负载，请与 `--no-enable-prefix-"
"caching` 进行比较。"

msgid "### Q3: How should I tune async scheduling for Qwen3.6?"
msgstr "### Q3：如何为 Qwen3.6 调整异步调度？"

msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** Throughput improves in high-concurrency scenarios, but some "
"latency-sensitive workloads may not benefit."
msgstr "**现象：** 在高并发场景下吞吐量提升，但某些延迟敏感型工作负载可能无法受益。"

msgid ""
"**Cause:** Asynchronous scheduling reduces blocking overhead, but the "
"benefit depends on concurrency, prompt/output length, and graph capture "
"shape."
msgstr "**原因：** 异步调度减少了阻塞开销，但其收益取决于并发度、提示/输出长度和图捕获形状。"

msgid ""
"**Solution:** Use `--async-scheduling` for high-throughput serving. For low-"
"latency serving, compare TTFT and TPOT with and without this option."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 对于高吞吐量服务，使用 `--async-scheduling`。对于低延迟服务，请比较启用和未启用此选项时的 TTFT 和 "
"TPOT。"

msgid ""
"| Scenario | Deployment Mode | Total NPUs | Weight Version | Key "
"Considerations |"
msgstr "| 场景 | 部署模式 | NPU总数 | 权重版本 | 关键考量 |"

msgid ""
"| Scenario | Node Role | NPUs | TP | DP | Max Num Seqs | Max Model Len | Max"
" Num Batched Tokens | Prefix Cache | Main Optimizations |"
msgstr ""
"| 场景 | 节点角色 | NPU数量 | TP | DP | 最大序列数 | 最大模型长度 | 最大批量Token数 | 前缀缓存 | 主要优化 |"

msgid "| Optimization | Enablement | Benefit | Notes |"
msgstr "| 优化项 | 启用方式 | 收益 | 备注 |"

msgid ""
"| Long context | Single-node online serving | 2 or more NPUs | W8A8 | Use "
"larger `--max-model-len` and reserve enough KV cache. Lower `--max-num-seqs`"
" if OOM occurs. |"
msgstr ""
"| 长上下文 | 单节点在线服务 | 2个或更多NPU | W8A8 | 使用更大的`--max-model-"
"len`并预留足够的KV缓存。如果发生OOM，则降低`--max-num-seqs`。 |"

msgid ""
"| High throughput | Single-node online serving | 8 or more NPUs | W8A8 | "
"Increase local DP groups within one node and tune `--max-num-batched-"
"tokens`. |"
msgstr ""
"| 高吞吐量 | 单节点在线服务 | 8个或更多NPU | W8A8 | 增加节点内的本地DP组，并调整`--max-num-batched-"
"tokens`。 |"

msgid ""
"| Low latency | Single-node online serving | 2 or more NPUs | W8A8 | Use "
"smaller `--max-num-batched-tokens`, full decode ACLGraph, and disable "
"speculative decoding by default. |"
msgstr ""
"| 低延迟 | 单节点在线服务 | 2个或更多NPU | W8A8 | 使用更小的`--max-num-batched-"
"tokens`、全解码ACLGraph，并默认禁用推测解码。 |"

msgid ""
"| Hybrid attention support | Enabled by model implementation | Supports "
"Qwen3.6 long-context inference. | Tune context length based on KV cache "
"capacity. |"
msgstr "| 混合注意力支持 | 由模型实现启用 | 支持Qwen3.6长上下文推理。 | 根据KV缓存容量调整上下文长度。 |"

msgid ""
"| Full decode ACLGraph | `--compilation-config "
"'{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` | Reduces operator dispatch "
"overhead and stabilizes decode performance. | Recommended for decode-heavy "
"serving. |"
msgstr ""
"| 全解码ACLGraph | `--compilation-config "
"'{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` | 减少算子分发开销，稳定解码性能。 | "
"推荐用于解码密集型服务。 |"

msgid ""
"| FlashComm1 | `--additional-config '{\"enable_flashcomm1\": true}'` | "
"Reduces communication overhead in TP and high-concurrency scenarios. | May "
"not help low-concurrency workloads. |"
msgstr ""
"| FlashComm1 | `--additional-config '{\"enable_flashcomm1\": true}'` | "
"减少TP和高并发场景下的通信开销。 | 可能对低并发工作负载无帮助。 |"

msgid ""
"| Shared expert overlap | `--additional-config "
"'{\"multistream_overlap_shared_expert\": true}'` | Overlaps shared expert "
"computation in MoE workloads. | Recommended for throughput scenarios. |"
msgstr ""
"| 共享专家重叠 | `--additional-config '{\"multistream_overlap_shared_expert\": "
"true}'` | 在MoE工作负载中重叠共享专家计算。 | 推荐用于吞吐量场景。 |"

msgid ""
"| Asynchronous scheduling | `--async-scheduling` | Improves high-concurrency"
" throughput by using non-blocking scheduling. | Disable it and compare if "
"the workload is latency-sensitive. |"
msgstr ""
"| 异步调度 | `--async-scheduling` | 通过非阻塞调度提高高并发吞吐量。 | 如果工作负载对延迟敏感，请禁用它并进行比较。 |"

msgid ""
"| Prefix caching | `--enable-prefix-caching` | Improves repeated-prefix "
"workloads. | Monitor HBM usage for long-context workloads. |"
msgstr ""
"| 前缀缓存 | `--enable-prefix-caching` | 改善重复前缀工作负载。 | 对于长上下文工作负载，监控HBM使用情况。 |"

msgid ""
"| Qwen3.6 MTP speculative decoding | `--speculative-config '{\"method\": "
"\"qwen3_5_mtp\", \"num_speculative_tokens\": 3, \"enforce_eager\": true}'` |"
" Can improve decode throughput when stable and accepted tokens are high. | "
"Validate stability, TTFT, TPOT, and throughput for your workload. |"
msgstr ""
"| Qwen3.6 MTP推测解码 | `--speculative-config '{\"method\": \"qwen3_5_mtp\", "
"\"num_speculative_tokens\": 3, \"enforce_eager\": true}'` | "
"当稳定且被接受的token数量较高时，可提高解码吞吐量。 | 验证工作负载的稳定性、TTFT、TPOT和吞吐量。 |"
